Class ModelExtractionStateImpl

java.lang.Object
edu.kit.kastel.informalin.framework.configuration.AbstractConfigurable
edu.kit.kastel.mcse.ardoco.core.api.data.AbstractState
edu.kit.kastel.mcse.ardoco.core.model.ModelExtractionStateImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
edu.kit.kastel.informalin.data.PipelineStepData, edu.kit.kastel.informalin.framework.configuration.IConfigurable, ModelExtractionState, Serializable
public class ModelExtractionStateImpl extends AbstractState implements ModelExtractionState
This state contains all from the model extracted information. This are the extracted instances and relations. For easier handling, the occurring types and names are stored additionally.
